  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nSince Quarkus 3.13.0, `QuarkusMainLauncher` always returns exit code `0` for integration tests and not the actual exit code.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nLooks like [this change](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/commit/485f45d9ce7b2a687ae5b81f8a58b158e7b3bafb#diff-26ee3c83ff30b212bba63973183542fc410eac597343bcaa20fea236fbc6c421) via #41726 made `QuarkusMainLauncher` always return exit code 0, because of [this check in `StartupActionImpl.runMainClassBlocking()`](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/5f35abd3d9ed04aed28a97803970604611806018/core/deployment/src/main/java/io/quarkus/runner/bootstrap/StartupActionImpl.java#L244)  \r\n\r\n/cc @gsmet \r\n\r\n### How to Reproduce?\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Output of `uname -a` or `ver`\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Output of `java -version`\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Quarkus version or git rev\r\n\r\n3.13.0\r\n\r\n### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\n_No response_",
